{"title":"Faerie dragon scales","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Faerie_dragon_scales","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |\n| - | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | An enchanted suit of armour created from the scales of a rare breed of dragon, now thought to be extinct. This prized relic is now one of the last proofs that the vividly coloured faerie dragons ever existed. |\n\n[![Faerie dragon armour.png](/images/b/b4/Faerie_dragon_armour.png)](/File:Faerie_dragon_armour.png) ***Faerie dragon scales***\n\n+X [acid dragon scales](/Acid_dragon_scales \"Acid dragon scales\") (ranges from 0 to +8)  \n[rCorr](/Acid#Corrosion \"Acid\")  \n1d3 random properties, with a chance of a negative property as well.\n\nThese random properties are selected much like the properties on [randart](/Randart \"Randart\") armour, though they are weighted toward being positive, and certain properties have adjusted likelihoods of occurring. The following properties are more likely to appear than average (5% chance of any given property being from this list):\n\n- [HP](/HP \"HP\") bonus (-10 to +11)\n- [MP](/MP \"MP\") bonus (+1 to +11)\n- [Clarity](/Clarity \"Clarity\")\n\n## Desirability\n\n**Faerie dragon scales**[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1) are a randomised artefact found only by killing [the Enchantress](/The_Enchantress \"The Enchantress\"). Its usefulness is entirely dependent on what the [RNG](/RNG \"RNG\") decides to generate.\n\nDon't overlook this armour until you've actually seen its properties. A set of +8 acid dragon scales with rF++, rElec, and Dex+10 is nothing to sneeze at. At the same time, heavy melee brutes will probably find this armour too light to wear.\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.19](/0.19 \"0.19\"), faerie dragon scales were called faerie dragon armour and the item's base type was mottled dragon armour.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [art-data.txt:375](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L375) (0.30.1)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Faerie dragon scales - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Faerie_dragon_scales\",\"wgTitle\":\"Faerie dragon scales\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":75844,\"wgRevisionId\":75844,\"wgArticleId\":9569,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Unrands\",\"Body armour\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Faerie_dragon_scales\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":9569,\"wgRequestId\":\"6467bd7e3d450d1a37c131b6\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestricti