 #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> An enchanted suit of armour created from the scales of a rare breed of dragon, now thought to be extinct. This prized relic is now one of the last proofs that the vividly coloured faerie dragons ever existed.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><a href=\"/File:Faerie_dragon_armour.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Faerie dragon armour.png\" src=\"/images/b/b4/Faerie_dragon_armour.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <i><b>Faerie dragon scales</b></i><br />\n</p><p>+X <a href=\"/Acid_dragon_scales\" title=\"Acid dragon scales\">acid dragon scales</a> (ranges from 0 to +8)<br />\n<a href=\"/Acid#Corrosion\" title=\"Acid\">rCorr</a><br />\n1d3 random properties, with a chance of a negative property as well.\n</p><p>These random properties are selected much like the properties on <a href=\"/Randart\" title=\"Randart\">randart</a> armour, though they are weighted toward being positive, and certain properties have adjusted likelihoods of occurring. The following properties are more likely to appear than average (5% chance of any given property being from this list):\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/HP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"HP\">HP</a> bonus (-10 to +11)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/MP\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"MP\">MP</a> bonus (+1 to +11)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Clarity\" title=\"Clarity\">Clarity</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desirability\">Desirability</span></h2>\n<p><b>Faerie dragon scales</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> are a randomised artefact found only by killing <a href=\"/The_Enchantress\" title=\"The Enchantress\">the Enchantress</a>. Its usefulness is entirely dependent on what the <a href=\"/RNG\" title=\"RNG\">RNG</a> decides to generate.\n</p><p>Don't overlook this armour until you've actually seen its properties. A set of +8 acid dragon scales with rF++, rElec, and Dex+10 is nothing to sneeze at. At the same time, heavy melee brutes will probably find this armour too light to wear.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.19\" title=\"0.19\">0.19</a>, faerie dragon scales were called faerie dragon armour and the item's base type was mottled dragon armour.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L375\">art-data.txt:375</a> (0.30.1)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916222920\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.097 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 212/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1502/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 253/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.010s\nLua virtual size: 8.02 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   70.213      1 -total\n 81.47%   57.205      1 Template:Version030\n 78.48%   55.101      1 Template:Version\n  2.66%    1.865      1 Template: